messages.text: Hi! I'm Anita Bhargava. Strategic wealth building with modern perspective. I'm here to help you understand your financial lifestyle and goals. To get started, could you please tell me your name?

messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Namaste! I'm Anita Bhargava, and I'm delighted to begin this financial journey with you. As a strategic wealth advisor with roots in Delhi and experience in New York's financial world, I bring a unique East-meets-West perspective to building sustainable wealth. Today, we'll explore your lifestyle aspirations and create a foundation for your financial success - because true wealth building starts with understanding your complete picture. Let's define success on your own terms. To begin, could you please share your name and age with me?
